reviewText: Even if you get it for free it isn't worth watching.

An outstanding DVD featuring great footage of Japan's fighter force. Featured are the F-15 Eagle, F-4 Phantom II, Mitsubishi F-1, F-104 Starfighter and the FS-X prototype which would become the Mitsubishi F-2. Worth checking out.

Very good dvd , with crisp and clear images and good sound.

Goes around several JASDF bases showing operations of F-15 and F-4.

The only remark: some commentary could be given to explain the missions shown.

Otherwise one of the best military avition DVD's I have seen.
